  "content": "<p data-pid=\"NNbxh1m4\">没有人推荐 Revue Starlight 吗？我的最爱——《少女☆歌剧 Revue Starlight》！</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-85731087ecbafe4086a30d39d1f7fbc7_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"900\" data-original-token=\"v2-85731087ecbafe4086a30d39d1f7fbc7\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-28f38ea2d3b6c93d76335cdb9304b060_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-85731087ecbafe4086a30d39d1f7fbc7_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;640&#39; height=&#39;900&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"900\" data-original-token=\"v2-85731087ecbafe4086a30d39d1f7fbc7\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-28f38ea2d3b6c93d76335cdb9304b060_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-85731087ecbafe4086a30d39d1f7fbc7_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-85731087ecbafe4086a30d39d1f7fbc7_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"0LpWlz-M\">第一集开头，我以为这是个日常番</p><p data-pid=\"tJaTtJ44\">第一集中间，这是个偶像百合啊（歌剧部又要废部了？一起成为偶像吧！）</p><p data-pid=\"jGCuYBFL\">第一集结尾，魔法少女？fate？？硬核战斗番！！！</p><p data-pid=\"9xQYckNd\">i 了 i 了，除了华丽的场面，配乐也非常喜欢。</p><p data-pid=\"a3kE-vy9\">前期的日常和战斗都让我十分偷税。</p><p data-pid=\"iK07ozp6\">每次更新都要守着，结果次次都是少女<b>鸽</b>剧，咕咕咕。</p><p data-pid=\"59xt7HYI\">中后期的剧情走向也十分给力，哇嘎力马斯！</p><p data-pid=\"N4iiGWjU\">在 B 站不需要会员也能看呢！</p><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.bilibili.com/bangumi/media/md102892\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-caffb70a3002805c71d16289092608fb_120x160.jpg\" data-image-width=\"480\" data-image-height=\"640\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">少女☆歌剧 Revue Starlight</a><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-032677b406467e711dd93682a0370087_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1393\" data-rawheight=\"468\" data-original-token=\"v2-032677b406467e711dd93682a0370087\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8f088e31b5a4bbf12b4ad9bbae7d4beb_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1393\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-032677b406467e711dd93682a0370087_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1393&#39; height=&#39;468&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1393\" data-rawheight=\"468\" data-original-token=\"v2-032677b406467e711dd93682a0370087\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8f088e31b5a4bbf12b4ad9bbae7d4beb_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1393\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-032677b406467e711dd93682a0370087_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-032677b406467e711dd93682a0370087_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"Dlp5oNRo\">专辑也很好听</p><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//music.163.com/album%3Fid%3D72383717%26userid%3D66053830\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2eb7940d1a6bf9d0735b83a002cbe6ef_ipico.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1257\" data-image-height=\"1257\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">「少女☆歌劇 レヴュースタァライト」劇中歌アルバムVol.1「ラ レヴュー ド マチネ」</a><p data-pid=\"oofVigtM\">对于对上电波的朋友，一集看个亿遍都不为过呢！</p>",
